data.title: Watch Bitter Jester Free
data.meta_description: BITTER JESTER is the first documentary giving us a real glimpse behind the comedy we watch in clubs, on TV and at the movies. Featuring Maija DiGiorgio, Kenneth Simmons, Richard Belzer, Whoopi Goldberg, Chevy Chase, Kevin James, Richard Pryor  many more.
